# .understandignore — patterns for files/dirs to exclude from analysis
# Syntax: same as .gitignore (globs, # comments, ! negation, trailing / for dirs)
#
# Scope: the ECC hook subsystem (reference/ECC-main/scripts/hooks) — a flat dir of
# ~48 hook scripts. Nothing to exclude here; built-in defaults (*.min.js, *.map,
# node_modules/, etc.) already cover the usual noise and none of it is present.
#
# Uncomment to exclude if desired:
# *.sh
# *.py
